President Donald J. Trump has announced his intent to nominate several individuals to key positions in his administration. Brian D. Miller is nominated to be the Special Inspector General for Pandemic Recovery at the Department of the Treasury. Peter M. Thomson is nominated to be the Inspector General for the Central Intelligence Agency. Katherine A. Crytzer is nominated to be the Inspector General for the Tennessee Valley Authority. Andrew A. De Mello is nominated to be the Inspector General for the Department of Education. Jason Abend is nominated to be the Inspector General for the Department of Defense. Each nominee has a background in law, government investigations, and/or corporate compliance.